Package edu.ntnu.idatt2001.runarin.frontend.model

Class ArmyWrapper

java.lang.Object
edu.ntnu.idatt2001.runarin.frontend.model.ArmyWrapper
public class ArmyWrapper extends Object
This class functions as a wrapper for the Army-class. The wrapper makes it possible to hold data from an army in an alternative format. In this case that means that the application view can update its numbers and list values compatible with a listener.
Since:
2022-05-18
